(g) bidi;
(h) handloom;
(i) hosiery;
(j) printing press;
(k) hotels or motels where number of guest rooms does not exceed
25 (twenty five);
(l) restaurant not forming part of a hotel;
(m) small-scale metal industry;
(n) book-binding;
(o) cinema and theatre;
(p) ship building;
(q) ship recycling;
(r) construction worker;
